Mr. and Mrs. Walker W. Stevenson Jr. of Princeton, N. J., and Nantucket, Mass., have announced here the en gagement of their daughter, Miss Sharon Stevenson, to Lieut. (jg.) Charles T. Griffith Jr., U.S.N. He is the son of Mr. and Mrs. Griffith of Brad ford, Pa.

The bride‐to‐be, a graphic artist with Alan M. Voorhees & Associates, transporation planning consultants, in San Diego, was graduated from Rosemary Hall in Greenwich, Conn., and from Briarcliff College. Her father is a senior partner in Hornblower & Weeks‐Hemphill, Noyes.

Lieutenant Griffith was graduated from the Asheville (N. C.) School, and in 1967 from Hamilton College. He is serving in the Western Pa cific, on the staff of Corn mender, Destroyer Division 52. His father is advertising manager of the Kendall Re fining Company.